-- Russia's FinMin to offer $3 bln at fx deposit auction on Dec. 15
-- By Yelena Orekhova
-- Fri Dec 12, 2014 02:35AM EST
-- None



MOSCOW, Dec 12 (Reuters) - Russia's Finance Ministry said on Friday it would offer $3 billion at a 14-day foreign-currency deposit auction on Dec. 15, as part of its efforts to ease pressure on the rouble.

